{"tid":2394074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"clubhouse語音系統由中國公司提供，愛國人士必用","createTime":"2021-02-04T02:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T15:27:54.000Z","uid":294343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa79f4c3fdf39cf3190db51ac449eee908793f3b","tid":2394074,"uid":294343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"見到有個post宣傳，咁多人要拎invitation code，就知連登大把人愛國，梗係要宣傳一齊用啦<br />\n<br />\nFervour over audio-focused social media start-up Clubhouse has sent shares of Chinese-founded company Agora soaring after news started circulating online that it was providing critical back-end communication services to the hottest new social app in Silicon Valley since Snapchat.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://amp.scmp.com/tech/start-ups/article/3120259/agora-chinese-company-powering-clubhouse-sees-stocks-soar-investors\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Famp.scmp.com%2Ftech%2Fstart-ups%2Farticle%2F3120259%2Fagora-chinese-company-powering-clubhouse-sees-stocks-soar-investors&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=804c0d8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://amp.scmp.com/tech/start-ups/article/3120259/agora-chinese-company-powering-clubhouse-sees-stocks-soar-investors</a><br />\n<br />\nInvestors could be playing up the privately held app&rsquo;s popularity by buying shares in&nbsp;Agora, which may have powered the app&rsquo;s livestreaming audio feature<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/01/agora-shares-soar-as-investors-try-to-jump-on-clubhouse-apps-growth.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2021%2F02%2F01%2Fagora-shares-soar-as-investors-try-to-jump-on-clubhouse-apps-growth.html&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=17e84fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/01/agora-shares-soar-as-investors-try-to-jump-on-clubhouse-apps-growth.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2nJTR2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2nJTR2C.jpg&h=e3146837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nClubhouse這個炙手可熱的社群平台，就是使用中國公司的服務；財經科技網站「Interconnected」創辦人Kevin Xu就直接發文，指Clubhouse是「建造在聲網上」。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCu0w1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCu0w1P.jpg&h=63ca762c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/146940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F146940&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=10dbcf88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/146940</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/01/agora-shares-soar-as-investors-try-to-jump-on-clubhouse-apps-growth.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2021%2F02%2F01%2Fagora-shares-soar-as-investors-try-to-jump-on-clubhouse-apps-growth.html&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=17e84fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/01/agora-shares-soar-as-investors-try-to-jump-on-clubhouse-apps-growth.html</a>"},{"pid":"18e8e54c89bf404a243a5477984f092a2af8ec21","tid":2394074,"uid":381835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d503f138d24d049d6ce4b49f95ad6a1090407cf7","tid":2394074,"uid":40165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:41:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d1a60ce698fd1b4597a466b59419709dd53169b","tid":2394074,"uid":294343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"自推吓先"},{"pid":"7e54274bcd6770b0588d0ba5e5cf308f5fab588f","tid":2394074,"uid":35658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:49:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b7dc7fcd109e0a1568231fa7dd8ca2206e988462","tid":2394074,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re